=Adeegsada=
[[Saddex xagal]]ka ayaa aad faa'iido u leh. Barashada joomatari ee la xidhiidha saddexagalka waxa loo yaqaan [[tirignoometeri]].  Dadka qaar ayaa noloshooda oo dhan ku qaatay barashada saddexagalka si loogu isticmaalo tirignoometeri.

[[Kumbuyuutar]]rada casriga ahi waxay inta badan adeegsadaan saddex xagal si ay u sameeyaan [[sawir]]ro garaafyo ama qaabab aad u adag.

